file.name: type_mapping_test.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Sample API to test type mapping
  description: API description in Markdown.
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /animals:
    get:
      summary: Returns all animals.
      description: Optional extended description in Markdown.
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: parameter_type_mapping
          schema:
            type: string 
            format: special
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Animal'
components:
  schemas:
    Animal:
      type: object
      required:
        - className
      properties:
        className:
          type: string
        color:
          type: string
          default: red
        mapping_test:
          type: string
          format: special
